cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO

This paper is about optimizing object detection in video streams, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a framework that involves machine learning and optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with real-time processing, which could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
